Hey all,

Due to an extremely small but critical misstep in the new filters/ 
common Makefile(.in), I present you cosign 1.9.2 ( MD5  
f75856d915e8c518c81b8ab70c48b7d7 )

It's got all the same yummy new goodness as 1.9.1, and will also  
build an apache filter that will transfer tickets. Thanks to Graeme  
Wood at University of Edinburgh for catching this. Which also brings  
me to my next question - anyone willing to test release candidates  
for us? I prefer to get things right the first time, and an extra  
pair of eyes is always helpful. Send me mail if you're interested and  
willing.

Thanks, and have a happy holiday for those of you who are celebrating  
tomorrow.

-Johanna, and the rest of the Cosign dev team

